            <bug_when>2010-08-04 09:29:25 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>The current implementation of the testrunner is really a grown system which can not handle the huge amount of tests we currently have in the framework. There are a couple of problem like load times, dependencies between different tests, ... 
Additionally, the code of the testrunner is not really maintainable anymore. We should rethink the whole concepts behind the current testrunner with especially scalability and maintainability in mind.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
